1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,539
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,539 --> 00:01:38,020
Episode 21

3
00:01:38,910 --> 00:01:39,789
Keep your hands like this.

4
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:41,539
Is it right?

5
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:42,360
Like this.

6
00:01:46,620 --> 00:01:50,220
(Script)

7
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,820
The tune you made

8
00:01:53,830 --> 00:01:55,789
is much better than the lyrics you modified.

9
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:59,180
It's just that I didn't go to school.

10
00:01:59,190 --> 00:02:01,110
Otherwise, my lyrics wouldn’t be that bad.

11
00:02:01,190 --> 00:02:01,580
Save it.

12
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:04,430
Perform your operas well.

13
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,620
Don’t do my job.

14
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:09,229
What are these symbols?

15
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:10,990
Are they drawn by Mr. Shang?

16
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,620
Don’t you understand?

17
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:16,870
This is Chinese musical notation,

18
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:19,660
namely the Chinese stave.

19
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:22,990
Leader.

20
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,780
Come here, everyone.

21
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,200
Quickly.

22
00:02:31,610 --> 00:02:32,230
Go.

23
00:02:34,790 --> 00:02:35,540
Hurry.

24
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,180
Shijiu. You go first.

25
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,590
OK.

26
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:54,880
♫ I’m favored by Your Majesty ♫

27
00:02:54,890 --> 00:03:01,430
♫ You put all your love on me ♫

28
00:03:01,650 --> 00:03:05,990
♫ However, I’m unlucky ♫

29
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,430
Stop. Stop.

30
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:12,150
You’re playing a chaste and fierce lady.

31
00:03:12,470 --> 00:03:14,180
How come it makes me shiver?

32
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:16,100
Ronglan. Your turn.

33
00:03:19,550 --> 00:03:20,510
Didn’t I sing well?

34
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:27,380
♫ I’m favored by Your Majesty ♫

35
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:32,990
♫ You put all your love ♫

36
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,020
Stop, sis.

37
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,230
Cut it out.

38
00:03:39,210 --> 00:03:40,430
How is it going?

39
00:03:41,140 --> 00:03:42,990
Hasn’t he chosen a concubine yet?

40
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,870
You’ve heard their voices.

41
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:48,540
Not good.

42
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,180
The strength is the key.

43
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:51,180
The strength isn’t right.

44
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:53,100
Leader, what do you mean the strength?

45
00:03:53,110 --> 00:03:53,950
Make it clear.

46
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,740
Well...

47
00:03:56,670 --> 00:03:58,510
I can't explain it to you.

48
00:04:00,050 --> 00:04:01,230
How should we perform then?

49
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,460
If it can’t do,

50
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:04,390
-we may invite someone from other troupes.
-Mr. Cheng.

51
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,590
We may pay more

52
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,100
to pick a good performer.

53
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,710
Let’s have an All-star Show.

54
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:11,590
Leader of opera circle will be voted next mouth.

55
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,710
All troupes will try their best to win.

56
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,510
How come they have time to support me?

57
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:18,110
How about you play the female role?

58
00:04:18,130 --> 00:04:19,709
Your strength is good enough.

59
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,029
Yes, leader.

60
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,220
Rob Peter to pay Paul?

61
00:04:23,350 --> 00:04:24,260
If I play the female role,

62
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:25,780
who would play the male role?

63
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:28,060
You? Or you?

64
00:04:29,550 --> 00:04:31,030
I’m unable to do that.

65
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,990
At this moment,

66
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:35,150
no opera performer

67
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:38,030
is willing to support other performers.

68
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,710
How about

69
00:04:40,550 --> 00:04:42,060
we look for an outsider?

70
00:04:42,230 --> 00:04:43,340
Outsider?

71
00:04:44,790 --> 00:04:46,100
You said this.

72
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,590
If moves are not considered,

73
00:04:49,110 --> 00:04:50,430
some outsiders

74
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:52,310
even sing better than leaders.

75
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,909
We have an outsider here.

76
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,470
Mr. Du.

77
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,780
-He is one of the best in Peking.
-Mr. Du?

78
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,150
Don’t. Don’t.

79
00:05:02,670 --> 00:05:04,470
Don't make fun of me.

80
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,870
My skills

81
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:07,630
can only fool laymen.

82
00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:09,870
If I can be a star,

83
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:11,500
how come

84
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:13,030
I humbly follow your leader

85
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,310
and write scripts for him?

86
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:16,430
Hi, guys.

87
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,380
Mr. Niu.

88
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,470
Mr. Niu.

89
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,220
Hello, Mr. Niu.

90
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,380
Hello, Mr. Cheng, Mr. Du.

91
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,310
Xiao Lai. Serve tea.

92
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,220
No. No.

93
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:23,630
No, thanks. Xiao Lai.

94
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,870
I’ll leave after my words.

95
00:05:25,050 --> 00:05:27,260
What’s wrong with the Opera Association this time?

96
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,190
Mr. Du.

97
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,150
Please don't joke about me.

98
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:33,430
Mr. Shang and you

99
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,380
made a scene in the Opera Association.

100
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,770
My gosh.

101
00:05:37,130 --> 00:05:38,659
Who dares to

102
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:40,030
mess with you now?

103
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:43,340
It’s just that

104
00:05:43,650 --> 00:05:45,260
Mr. Yuan Xiaodi will retire.

105
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,310
He invites you for a banquet

106
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:50,010
in the Opera Association next week.

107
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,590
What?

108
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:53,030
Will Mr. Yuan retire?

109
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:55,030
Yes, he meant to quit long ago.

110
00:05:55,659 --> 00:05:57,820
He hasn’t performed much these years.

111
00:05:58,570 --> 00:06:00,340
His wife is pregnant

112
00:06:00,350 --> 00:06:02,220
and his satin shop opens,

113
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:03,940
so it’s put off until now.

114
00:06:04,580 --> 00:06:06,910
Mr. Du, Mr. Cheng, would you go together?

115
00:06:07,540 --> 00:06:08,940
(Mr. Shang Xirui)

116
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,780
I won’t.

117
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:12,940
Yuan Xiaodi is phony.

118
00:06:12,950 --> 00:06:14,310
I don’t like him.

119
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:15,710
Well, Mr. Du.

120
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:17,380
Alright. Mr. Shang.

121
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,190
I have to visit others.

122
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:22,070
Mr. Cheng. Mr. Du. Goodbye.

123
00:06:23,350 --> 00:06:24,470
Mr. Niu, take care.

124
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:26,390
Take care, Mr. Niu.

125
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:29,780
What a pity.

126
00:06:29,790 --> 00:06:31,100
What a pity it is.

127
00:06:31,510 --> 00:06:32,960
Who is Yuan Xiaodi?

128
00:06:33,940 --> 00:06:35,590
I’ve never heard of him.

129
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,780
I only watched

130
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:39,500
two operas of Mr. Yuan.

131
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,380
That’s amazing.

132
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:43,500
Since I came to Peking,

133
00:06:43,730 --> 00:06:45,570
the most regrettable thing is

134
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:47,060
that Hou Yukui retires.

135
00:06:47,810 --> 00:06:49,990
Mr. Hou is old indeed,

136
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,710
but Yuan Xiaodi isn’t.

137
00:06:52,790 --> 00:06:54,710
I’ve been looking forward to

138
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:57,380
performing with him someday.

139
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:02,190
I wish I’d have come to Peking earlier.

140
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,590
You’re too young to understand.

141
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,060
You'll understand it in the future.

142
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:19,870
You’re back.

143
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:22,820
Your brother hasn't seen you for days.

144
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:24,060
Go talk to him.

145
00:07:25,790 --> 00:07:26,750
Why did you lie to me?

146
00:07:27,950 --> 00:07:28,540
Chacha’er.

147
00:07:28,810 --> 00:07:30,100
What did I just tell you?

148
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,470
Did I lie to you?

149
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,820
You sent Ge to pick up Zheng Laihong and me

150
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:40,820
so as to take him hostage.

151
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:42,659
You mean the young master of Zheng family?

152
00:07:43,550 --> 00:07:45,820
I didn’t hurt him at all.

153
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:46,940
You threatened his grandfather

154
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,310
with him,

155
00:07:48,610 --> 00:07:49,870
so, his grandfather was arrested.

156
00:07:50,450 --> 00:07:51,560
I’ve told you

157
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:53,530
it’s not your brother's fault.

158
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:57,400
Darling, go to your room first.

159
00:07:57,970 --> 00:07:59,810
I'd like to talk with Chacha’er alone.

160
00:08:01,450 --> 00:08:03,680
Talk properly. Don’t get mad.

161
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:21,530
Be seated.

162
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,210
Let me ask you.

163
00:08:50,010 --> 00:08:51,680
Zheng Laihong and I,

164
00:08:52,300 --> 00:08:53,560
whose life is more important?

165
00:08:53,570 --> 00:08:54,650
Yours, of course.

166
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:57,680
That’s it.

167
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:00,480
I was surrounded

168
00:09:00,930 --> 00:09:02,410
by a dozen armed men.

169
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:05,290
I almost didn’t make it to see you alive.

170
00:09:07,370 --> 00:09:08,480
Hadn’t I used him,

171
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:10,360
how could I get back in one piece?

172
00:09:12,540 --> 00:09:13,170
Of course.

173
00:09:14,610 --> 00:09:15,910
I shouldn’t have lied to you.

174
00:09:16,980 --> 00:09:17,970
I won’t do it again.

175
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:19,530
Alright?

176
00:09:20,610 --> 00:09:21,730
You told me

177
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:24,210
his grandfather’s matter wouldn’t implicate him.

178
00:09:25,770 --> 00:09:27,360
His grandfather was arrested.

179
00:09:28,370 --> 00:09:30,770
He will go to hometown with his parents.

180
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:32,680
It's none of my business.

181
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:33,770
But...

182
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:34,530
Chacha’er.

183
00:09:38,610 --> 00:09:40,890
When father died,

184
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:44,040
debtors came to collect money.

185
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:46,480
The three of us

186
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:48,940
led a terrifying life. You remember?

187
00:09:51,450 --> 00:09:52,310
At that time,

188
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:55,120
no one came to tell us

189
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:58,600
father’s debt shouldn’t implicate children.

190
00:10:02,370 --> 00:10:04,890
Zheng enjoyed benefits from his grandfather.

191
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,560
His grandfather falls from power.

192
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:09,090
He must suffer the equivalent pain.

193
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:11,290
It’s unquestionable.

194
00:10:11,490 --> 00:10:12,440
Fengtai.

195
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:15,120
What?

196
00:10:17,490 --> 00:10:18,680
You've changed.

197
00:10:19,450 --> 00:10:21,560
You’re not the same as you were in Shanghai.

198
00:10:25,310 --> 00:10:26,890
If I were still the same,

199
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:29,480
how could I support this family

200
00:10:30,010 --> 00:10:31,240
and protect you?

201
00:10:32,050 --> 00:10:32,800
Fengtai.

202
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:42,680
You will also get changed

203
00:10:43,930 --> 00:10:45,210
when you grow up.

204
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:17,720
Morning, Mr. Cheng.

205
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:22,210
Mr. Shang, you’re well dressed.

206
00:11:25,340 --> 00:11:26,800
This dress

207
00:11:27,430 --> 00:11:28,680
suits you well.

208
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:31,730
When we eat in a while,

209
00:11:31,740 --> 00:11:32,730
be elegant.

210
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,390
Change the way when eating.

211
00:11:34,590 --> 00:11:36,270
Don’t frighten Yuan Xiaodi.

212
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:38,580
I’m very elegant to outsiders usually.

213
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:42,430
Look at my fan.

214
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:44,390
It’s drawn by Mr. Du's father.

215
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,660
You can’t buy it with money.

216
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:48,430
Save it. Stop showing off.

217
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,430
Let's go now.

218
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:55,580
I just need a little.

219
00:11:55,590 --> 00:11:56,270
It smells good.

220
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:57,660
I’m scared to death.

221
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:59,580
I thought someone threw a bomb.

222
00:12:03,590 --> 00:12:06,220
His hands are good.

223
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:07,510
Really good.

224
00:12:08,330 --> 00:12:09,310
Gentlemen.

225
00:12:10,010 --> 00:12:10,800
Mr. Shang.

226
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:12,770
Long time no see. Long time no see.

227
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:13,970
Cheng.

228
00:12:14,660 --> 00:12:16,600
Do you come with an invitation?

229
00:12:18,130 --> 00:12:20,120
No seat for you later.

230
00:12:21,930 --> 00:12:24,240
I’m here to serve Mr. Shang.

231
00:12:26,690 --> 00:12:27,730
Cheng.

232
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,890
If you could be kind to me

233
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:31,650
as much as to my little finger,

234
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,410
I would be satisfied.

235
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:38,120
Look.

236
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:39,760
Mr. Shang is having chat

237
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:40,850
with other leaders.

238
00:12:41,220 --> 00:12:42,210
He has no time for you.

239
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:44,470
Mr. Sixi’er comes.

240
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:56,890
So many people here.

241
00:12:59,180 --> 00:13:01,800
All the opera stars are here.

242
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:03,560
It’s rare to see.

243
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:06,380
(Sixi’er)

244
00:13:07,690 --> 00:13:08,360
Who is

245
00:13:08,370 --> 00:13:09,680
this annoying guy?

246
00:13:10,130 --> 00:13:11,120
He is

247
00:13:12,220 --> 00:13:13,960
Sixi’er from Yunxi Theater.

248
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:15,530
A buffoon.

249
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:17,360
Gentlemen.

250
00:13:17,450 --> 00:13:19,370
How is your business going?

251
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:23,050
Will you participate in the election of leader?

252
00:13:23,810 --> 00:13:24,560
Mr. Shang.

253
00:13:25,130 --> 00:13:26,700
Your royal theater is really gorgeous.

254
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:27,530
(Zhouzi)
Your royal theater is really gorgeous.

255
00:13:27,530 --> 00:13:27,760
(Zhouzi)

256
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:29,180
Will you invite us to perform together?
(Zhouzi)

257
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:29,920
Will you invite us to perform together?

258
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:32,410
That will be my honor.

259
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:40,090
Isn’t this the famous Mr. Shang?

260
00:13:40,370 --> 00:13:42,480
It’s said you’re of good looking and temperament.

261
00:13:43,980 --> 00:13:46,090
I never thought you’d be plain off stage.

262
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:47,770
Guess what.

263
00:13:48,220 --> 00:13:49,530
In the crowd,

264
00:13:49,810 --> 00:13:51,770
I didn’t even see you.

265
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:54,480
That’s my fault.

266
00:13:55,130 --> 00:13:57,680
That voice still isn’t good.

267
00:13:58,130 --> 00:13:59,970
Don’t use the Flower-selling Tune.

268
00:13:59,980 --> 00:14:00,850
When I go back,

269
00:14:00,980 --> 00:14:02,680
I’ll discuss with Mr. Du.

270
00:14:02,690 --> 00:14:04,440
Don’t worry.

271
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:05,850
OK. OK.

272
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:09,850
Mr. Shang, you ignored me.

273
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:12,000
It's understandable.

274
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:13,290
Mr. Shang

275
00:14:13,310 --> 00:14:15,210
lives off Commander Cao’s brother-in-law,

276
00:14:15,330 --> 00:14:17,240
and sees a high-ranking official as godfather.

277
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,360
A sparrow becomes a phoenix.

278
00:14:20,420 --> 00:14:22,090
Serve him in a careful way.

279
00:14:22,410 --> 00:14:23,190
Mr. Shang

280
00:14:23,210 --> 00:14:24,970
even looks down on Mr. Jiang.

281
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:27,290
Not to mention humble guys like us.

282
00:14:27,740 --> 00:14:29,360
If we offend him with any word,

283
00:14:29,980 --> 00:14:32,480
he may take soldiers to bring down the troupes.

284
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,650
What's wrong with this guy?

285
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:34,850
Cheng. Cheng.

286
00:14:35,130 --> 00:14:37,170
Don’t mess with these performers.

287
00:14:37,180 --> 00:14:38,170
It’d get worse.

288
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:39,250
What are you guys talking about?

289
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:40,980
So lively.

290
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:46,620
(Yu Qing)

291
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:48,170
I wondered who it was.
(Yu Qing)

292
00:14:48,370 --> 00:14:50,210
It is Ms. Yu Qing.

293
00:14:50,780 --> 00:14:51,410
Yu Qing?

294
00:14:53,610 --> 00:14:54,680
The fan

295
00:14:55,450 --> 00:14:58,170
who was unwilling to be General Zhao’s concubine?

296
00:14:59,250 --> 00:15:00,890
Impressive, Cheng.

297
00:15:01,370 --> 00:15:03,050
You even know Yu Qing?

298
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:05,560
It was reported in newspaper.

299
00:15:06,450 --> 00:15:07,530
A talented woman.

300
00:15:08,130 --> 00:15:11,650
Ms. Yu, the journey must be tiring.

301
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:13,890
You’re too kind.

302
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:16,090
You’re elder than me over 20 years.

303
00:15:16,610 --> 00:15:18,410
I should pay respects to you.

304
00:15:22,690 --> 00:15:23,970
Ms. Yu, you’re polite.

305
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:25,830
I dare not be your senior.

306
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:31,530
Ms. Yu comes to Peking.

307
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:34,170
It does grace the imperial capital.

308
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,330
In my opinion,

309
00:15:35,540 --> 00:15:37,040
Ms. Yu’s beauty and temperament

310
00:15:37,050 --> 00:15:38,890
are unparalleled.

311
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:42,290
No wonder General Zhao only wants to marry you.

312
00:15:43,660 --> 00:15:44,920
It has passed.

313
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:47,000
Don’t talk about it anymore.

314
00:15:47,450 --> 00:15:49,360
You are from a wealthy family,

315
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:50,950
so you remain unchanged in poverty.

316
00:15:51,570 --> 00:15:52,600
If someone else

317
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:54,330
met a powerful general,

318
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:56,730
they’d definitely marry him.

319
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:57,920
I am

320
00:15:57,930 --> 00:15:59,480
hot-tempered and sharp-tongued.

321
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:02,410
I like satirizing people for no reason.

322
00:16:03,340 --> 00:16:05,530
I’m also jealous of those who are better than me.

323
00:16:06,780 --> 00:16:09,480
As they said, you’re kind of like me.

324
00:16:12,340 --> 00:16:13,800
You know,

325
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:15,650
with a temper like this,

326
00:16:16,540 --> 00:16:18,730
when we deal with the powerful nobles

327
00:16:19,010 --> 00:16:20,290
long,

328
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:22,560
they will slap me for sure.

329
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:31,100
(Master)

330
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:31,920
Zhouzi.
(Master)

331
00:16:34,780 --> 00:16:36,530
You shameless good-for-nothing.

332
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:38,090
You’re rude at home while coward outside.

333
00:16:38,420 --> 00:16:39,560
Do what you should do.

334
00:16:39,570 --> 00:16:40,770
Mr. Hong is waiting for you.

335
00:16:42,450 --> 00:16:44,290
Yes, leader. I’m going right away.

336
00:16:49,810 --> 00:16:50,850
Go.

337
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:57,450
Cheng.

338
00:16:58,490 --> 00:17:01,090
These guys are even worse than those in Shuiyun.

339
00:17:04,460 --> 00:17:06,240
Mr. Shang is a good manager.

340
00:17:06,770 --> 00:17:08,650
Shuiyun Theater is in harmony.

341
00:17:09,250 --> 00:17:11,050
No one else is comparable.

342
00:17:13,849 --> 00:17:14,810
Mr. Shang.

343
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:16,770
Nice to meet you.

344
00:17:17,730 --> 00:17:19,000
Ms. Yu, you know me?

345
00:17:19,940 --> 00:17:21,890
You’re well-known, Mr. Shang.

346
00:17:22,730 --> 00:17:24,109
I plan to watch your shows

347
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:25,579
for one month

348
00:17:25,609 --> 00:17:27,040
in Peking.

349
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:28,119
I’ve specially prepared

350
00:17:28,410 --> 00:17:30,290
a large sum of money for tickets.

351
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:31,650
You’re too kind.

352
00:17:31,660 --> 00:17:33,320
I should offer you tickets for free.

353
00:17:33,660 --> 00:17:34,530
Right.

354
00:17:34,780 --> 00:17:36,960
Whenever you come to watch operas,

355
00:17:37,130 --> 00:17:38,720
I’ll get the best box ready for you.

356
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:41,530
This is Mr. Cheng Fengtai,

357
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:42,960
the investor of Shuiyun Theater.

358
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:45,530
This is...

359
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:47,600
Fan Lian, the manager of Shuiyun Theater.

360
00:17:55,940 --> 00:17:56,600
Mr. Yuan.

361
00:17:56,610 --> 00:17:57,450
Hello, gentlemen.

362
00:17:57,730 --> 00:17:58,600
Long time no see.

363
00:17:58,780 --> 00:17:59,240
Mr. Yuan.

364
00:17:59,250 --> 00:17:59,460
Long time no see, Mr. Zhang.

365
00:17:59,460 --> 00:18:00,200
(Yuan Xiaodi)
Long time no see, Mr. Zhang.

366
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:00,970
(Yuan Xiaodi)

367
00:18:00,970 --> 00:18:01,450
Mr. Yuan.
(Yuan Xiaodi)

368
00:18:01,450 --> 00:18:01,700
(Yuan Xiaodi)

369
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:02,930
It’s been a while, Mr. Li.
(Yuan Xiaodi)

370
00:18:02,930 --> 00:18:03,420
(Yuan Xiaodi)

371
00:18:04,610 --> 00:18:05,960
Cheng, I drank too much water.

372
00:18:05,970 --> 00:18:07,360
I’m going to the toilet.

373
00:18:07,370 --> 00:18:08,690
Lazy guys go to toilets frequently.

374
00:18:08,700 --> 00:18:10,170
You may chat first.

375
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:14,410
Mr. Yuan. All the leaders have arrived.

376
00:18:14,730 --> 00:18:15,450
They’re waiting.

377
00:18:42,210 --> 00:19:18,170
♫ When I was 16 years old, I met the noble ♫

378
00:19:18,180 --> 00:19:26,170
♫ When I was 16 years old, I met the noble ♫

379
00:19:26,820 --> 00:19:28,080
Thank you

380
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:30,220
for coming to my banquet.

381
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:33,060
I’ve been in the opera circle most of my lifetime.

382
00:19:34,760 --> 00:19:36,510
I made a living

383
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:37,820
under your help.

384
00:19:38,760 --> 00:19:41,340
Now I want to start a new life.

385
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:43,670
I feel panicked.

386
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:46,060
So, I still count on you

387
00:19:46,070 --> 00:19:46,980
to take care of me in the future.

388
00:19:47,790 --> 00:19:49,340
Although I’ve left the opera circle,

389
00:19:49,610 --> 00:19:51,030
we’re still good friends.

390
00:19:53,190 --> 00:19:53,670
Please.

391
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:55,990
My toast to you.

392
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:01,250
To Mr. Yuan.

393
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:17,220
Mr. Shang.

394
00:20:17,430 --> 00:20:19,220
This is your favorite pork joint.

395
00:20:25,820 --> 00:20:27,750
Break it with chopsticks.

396
00:20:36,230 --> 00:20:37,580
You must be Mr. Shang.

397
00:20:37,620 --> 00:20:38,910
Mr. Yuan. Do you know me?

398
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:40,060
Yes.

399
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:42,580
Your performance is really amazing.

400
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:44,180
Other than Peking Opera,

401
00:20:44,760 --> 00:20:46,220
even your Kun opera is excellent.

402
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:49,910
I was lucky to watch your Peony Pavilion.

403
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,180
I didn’t dare to sing when I got back.

404
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:53,460
It's very kind of you.

405
00:20:53,470 --> 00:20:54,870
I'm far away from that.

406
00:20:55,110 --> 00:20:56,790
You’re too modest, Mr. Shang.

407
00:20:57,070 --> 00:20:58,060
For example,

408
00:20:58,230 --> 00:20:59,820
this spoken line:

409
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:00,990
If I don’t come to the garden,

410
00:21:01,190 --> 00:21:02,790
how can I know the spring is so beautiful?

411
00:21:03,180 --> 00:21:05,910
You did speak out the bright spring.

412
00:21:06,430 --> 00:21:07,990
I think the Black Rope after it

413
00:21:08,430 --> 00:21:09,790
was redundant.

414
00:21:10,040 --> 00:21:11,030
I’m flattered.

415
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,940
After all, I'm still young.

416
00:21:12,950 --> 00:21:14,300
My skills are not good enough.

417
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:15,420
Besides,

418
00:21:15,430 --> 00:21:16,670
The Black Rope

419
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:18,180
has good lyrics.

420
00:21:18,460 --> 00:21:19,910
How come they’re redundant?

421
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:22,180
Right.

422
00:21:22,900 --> 00:21:24,200
Not redundant really.

423
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:26,650
Spoken lines

424
00:21:26,820 --> 00:21:28,340
come before the lyrics.

425
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:30,810
If you read the spoken lines well,

426
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:32,170
the artistic mood

427
00:21:32,450 --> 00:21:33,960
would be shown without singing.

428
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:36,240
You have a point.

429
00:21:36,660 --> 00:21:37,770
I toast you.

430
00:22:04,010 --> 00:22:05,120
Everyone.

431
00:22:09,290 --> 00:22:09,960
Everyone.

432
00:22:11,610 --> 00:22:12,960
It’s lively today.

433
00:22:13,330 --> 00:22:15,230
We come here for Mr. Yuan.

434
00:22:15,900 --> 00:22:17,960
So, Mr. Yuan should make a show. Right?

435
00:22:18,580 --> 00:22:19,650
After

436
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:22,020
Mr. Yuan retires,

437
00:22:22,370 --> 00:22:24,400
you can no longer watch his shows.

438
00:22:24,900 --> 00:22:26,050
Good.

439
00:22:26,180 --> 00:22:27,320
Make a show!

440
00:22:27,660 --> 00:22:29,000
Make a show! Make a show!

441
00:22:29,010 --> 00:22:30,360
Mr. Yuan, make a show.

442
00:22:31,790 --> 00:22:32,720
Alright.

443
00:22:33,580 --> 00:22:34,720
I’ll perform then.

444
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:36,720
What would you watch?

445
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:39,050
We’re tired of Peking Opera.

446
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,940
Mr. Shang had a hot talk

447
00:22:40,950 --> 00:22:42,300
about Peony Pavilion.

448
00:22:42,560 --> 00:22:44,700
How about you two perform Awakened Dream?

449
00:22:54,860 --> 00:22:56,500
-What’s going on?
-What’s wrong with Mr. Shang?

450
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:58,030
Mr. Shang.

451
00:22:59,230 --> 00:23:00,180
Mr. Shang.

452
00:23:00,590 --> 00:23:02,420
Tell me. Would you sing or not?

453
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:04,180
I’m drunk. I’m Drunk.

454
00:23:04,190 --> 00:23:05,150
I can’t sing.

455
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,550
I drank too much.

456
00:23:08,950 --> 00:23:10,930
I’m afraid I’d sing Du Li’niang into Yang Paifeng

457
00:23:10,940 --> 00:23:12,870
and beat Mr. Xi.

458
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,670
Sheng is rude indeed,

459
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:16,820
even if he plays female roles.

460
00:23:17,430 --> 00:23:18,390
Mr. Shang would slap me

461
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,820
to death.

462
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:22,700
Everyone.

463
00:23:23,710 --> 00:23:25,150
Since Mr. Shang is drunk,

464
00:23:25,420 --> 00:23:26,410
don’t let him sing.

465
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,240
I’ll take him to sober up.

466
00:23:29,700 --> 00:23:30,480
Excuse me.

467
00:23:35,010 --> 00:23:36,450
Are they leaving?

468
00:23:36,940 --> 00:23:38,530
Don’t leave. Mr. Shang.

469
00:23:38,820 --> 00:23:40,600
Mr. Shang. Mr. Shang.

470
00:23:41,010 --> 00:23:42,120
Everyone.

471
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:45,720
Let Mr. Xi

472
00:23:45,730 --> 00:23:47,170
perform for us. Alright?

473
00:23:47,930 --> 00:23:49,200
Sure!

474
00:23:50,180 --> 00:23:51,890
Make a show!

475
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:55,120
I can’t.

476
00:23:55,130 --> 00:23:56,570
My voice

477
00:23:56,580 --> 00:23:58,000
is no match to Mr. Yuan’s.

478
00:24:00,490 --> 00:24:02,120
Let Ms. Yu perform.

479
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:04,960
Ms. Yu is Mr. Yuan’s favorite apprentice.

480
00:24:05,190 --> 00:24:06,890
She became a performer for Mr. Yuan.

481
00:24:07,060 --> 00:24:08,740
Ms. Yu is best

482
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:11,170
at matching with Mr. Yuan.

483
00:24:13,490 --> 00:24:14,690
Ms. Yu had a tiring journey.

484
00:24:15,260 --> 00:24:16,770
She is too tired to perform.

485
00:24:16,780 --> 00:24:18,490
Taking car is tiring?

486
00:24:18,780 --> 00:24:19,810
We still performed

487
00:24:19,820 --> 00:24:21,120
even when parents died.

488
00:24:22,820 --> 00:24:25,410
I forget Ms. Yu’s identity.

489
00:24:26,210 --> 00:24:27,720
She plays opera for fun.

490
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:29,000
Anyway,

491
00:24:29,460 --> 00:24:31,480
she’s nobler than performers.

492
00:24:33,250 --> 00:24:34,050
Mr. Xi.

493
00:24:34,060 --> 00:24:34,890
You are drunk.

494
00:24:34,900 --> 00:24:35,170
Go. Go.

495
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:36,570
Let me take you to sober up.

496
00:24:36,700 --> 00:24:37,350
Mr. Niu.

497
00:24:38,580 --> 00:24:39,810
Don’t you understand?

498
00:24:40,850 --> 00:24:42,290
Mr. Xi

499
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:44,410
wants to keep me here.

500
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,080
If I don’t sing,

501
00:24:48,210 --> 00:24:50,530
all the leaders here will lose face.

502
00:24:54,820 --> 00:24:55,480
Mr. Yuan.

503
00:24:56,750 --> 00:24:58,200
We haven’t performed together for long.

504
00:24:58,610 --> 00:25:01,570
We won't have a chance you retire.

505
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:03,410
Today,

506
00:25:04,610 --> 00:25:07,480
let’s have a show together.

507
00:25:13,970 --> 00:25:15,050
OK. Ms. Yu.

508
00:25:16,850 --> 00:25:18,080
I’ll support you as Sheng.

509
00:25:22,530 --> 00:25:23,650
You’re heavy.

510
00:25:24,820 --> 00:25:26,120
Sober up. Sober up.

511
00:25:26,730 --> 00:25:28,720
Open your eyes. Stop acting.

512
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:31,050
You should be more sincere.

513
00:25:31,250 --> 00:25:33,120
Is Sixi’er nuts?

514
00:25:33,850 --> 00:25:35,410
I wanted to curse him

515
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:36,930
and slap him.

516
00:25:37,730 --> 00:25:38,710
If we were not

517
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:40,290
at Mr. Yuan’s banquet,

518
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:41,810
I wouldn’t have spared him.

519
00:25:42,060 --> 00:25:43,560
-I would...
-Fine. Fine.

520
00:25:44,130 --> 00:25:45,170
I know.

521
00:25:45,180 --> 00:25:48,730
You’re aware of occasion and manners.

522
00:25:49,050 --> 00:25:51,320
You even pretended drunk to avoid troubles.

523
00:25:52,460 --> 00:25:54,650
Good. You’ve grown up.

524
00:25:55,110 --> 00:25:56,240
I’m relieved.

525
00:25:58,900 --> 00:25:59,720
Cheng.

526
00:26:01,130 --> 00:26:02,530
You act to be my senior

527
00:26:02,540 --> 00:26:03,690
and take advantage of me again.

528
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:41,540
♫ Afraid to see the lonely boat ♫

529
00:26:41,540 --> 00:27:15,460
♫ There’s unspeakable pain at departure ♫

530
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:37,940
♫ Hate to be parted instantly ♫

531
00:27:38,340 --> 00:28:07,300
♫ My heart and eyes bleed ♫

532
00:28:07,860 --> 00:28:13,180
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

533
00:28:13,180 --> 00:28:14,100
What are you doing?
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

534
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:15,460
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

535
00:28:15,460 --> 00:28:17,050
That’s my question.
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

536
00:28:17,050 --> 00:28:17,540
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

537
00:28:17,540 --> 00:28:18,530
You seemed bewitched
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

538
00:28:18,530 --> 00:28:18,540
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

539
00:28:18,540 --> 00:28:19,770
and didn’t answer me.
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

540
00:28:19,770 --> 00:28:22,420
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

541
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:23,290
Cheng.
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

542
00:28:23,290 --> 00:28:24,130
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

543
00:28:24,130 --> 00:28:26,080
I want to invite Yu Qing for the Tale of Dragon.
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

544
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:26,900
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

545
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,050
It must be her.
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

546
00:28:28,050 --> 00:28:28,620
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

547
00:28:28,620 --> 00:28:29,480
I don’t want anyone else.
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

548
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:36,260
♫ Get pinched due to sorrow ♫

549
00:28:37,330 --> 00:28:40,320
Ms. Yu is a lady

550
00:28:41,010 --> 00:28:42,810
from a famous family.

551
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:45,930
You’re pretty,

552
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:48,810
and talk pretty words,

553
00:28:49,610 --> 00:28:52,720
and you’re educated and well-mannered.

554
00:28:53,170 --> 00:28:54,050
-What...
-Cheng.

555
00:28:54,060 --> 00:28:54,720
Look.

556
00:28:55,250 --> 00:28:56,720
Someone seduces you

557
00:28:57,660 --> 00:29:00,080
and you also lick shoes.

558
00:29:00,360 --> 00:29:02,120
How come you believe the groundless rumor?

559
00:29:02,540 --> 00:29:03,310
(Mrs. Yuan)

560
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:04,790
Mrs. Yuan. You mistook it.
(Mrs. Yuan)

561
00:29:04,790 --> 00:29:05,980
(Mrs. Yuan)

562
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:07,120
I come Peking
(Mrs. Yuan)

563
00:29:08,690 --> 00:29:09,960
not for Ms. Yuan.

564
00:29:10,180 --> 00:29:11,570
Right. Ms. Yuan.

565
00:29:11,940 --> 00:29:13,070
It’s my fault.

566
00:29:13,700 --> 00:29:16,360
I have a big mouth.

567
00:29:17,250 --> 00:29:18,930
Don’t take it to heart.

568
00:29:19,090 --> 00:29:20,840
They just performed.

569
00:29:21,900 --> 00:29:23,240
How come they quarreled all of a sudden?

570
00:29:23,490 --> 00:29:24,360
With whom?

571
00:29:24,460 --> 00:29:26,650
It’s Sixi’er who stirred things up.

572
00:29:26,940 --> 00:29:29,790
He asked Yuan and Yu Qing to perform together.

573
00:29:30,060 --> 00:29:32,050
Mrs. Yuan knew Yu Qing was here

574
00:29:32,060 --> 00:29:33,200
and ran into

575
00:29:33,630 --> 00:29:35,650
that they were performing together.

576
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:36,960
She flipped.

577
00:29:37,210 --> 00:29:38,530
She's pregnant,

578
00:29:38,610 --> 00:29:39,930
and still hot-tempered.

579
00:29:40,390 --> 00:29:41,250
What?

580
00:29:41,970 --> 00:29:43,600
I got it right.

581
00:29:45,210 --> 00:29:46,890
Hadn’t I come,

582
00:29:47,130 --> 00:29:47,500
would you

583
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:49,380
let them drink like a couple?

584
00:29:49,390 --> 00:29:50,290
What are you talking about?

585
00:29:51,330 --> 00:29:52,480
We just performed.

586
00:29:52,850 --> 00:29:54,050
Her operas were all taught by me.

587
00:29:56,370 --> 00:29:58,420
So, you are her master.

588
00:29:59,070 --> 00:30:00,790
Then I’m her mistress.

589
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:04,690
Why do you still call me Mrs. Yuan?

590
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,930
Call me mistress.

591
00:30:09,700 --> 00:30:11,050
I want to hear it.

592
00:30:15,090 --> 00:30:16,650
Why don’t you call me?

593
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:27,500
Yuan Xiaodi is so coward.

594
00:30:29,250 --> 00:30:30,290
I’ll go to help.

595
00:30:32,730 --> 00:30:34,050
You can help him,

596
00:30:34,300 --> 00:30:37,080
but be aware of your manners in public.

597
00:30:38,130 --> 00:30:39,480
I'm a man of letters.

598
00:30:42,780 --> 00:30:45,530
Only one thing Mr. Xi said is right.

599
00:30:46,250 --> 00:30:46,930
You

600
00:30:47,150 --> 00:30:49,050
do have a big mouth.

601
00:30:49,610 --> 00:30:51,890
Ms. Yu is invited by me

602
00:30:51,910 --> 00:30:53,410
to perform my new opera with me.

603
00:30:54,250 --> 00:30:56,580
Although Yuan is the host today,

604
00:30:56,820 --> 00:30:58,080
you shouldn’t let them perform together

605
00:30:58,090 --> 00:30:59,720
without my consent.

606
00:31:02,460 --> 00:31:04,530
Mr. Shang, you sober up so soon.

607
00:31:05,510 --> 00:31:06,810
Is that true?

608
00:31:08,780 --> 00:31:10,170
I didn’t hear of that.

609
00:31:10,610 --> 00:31:11,690
Hear of my things?

610
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:13,890
You don’t deserve it.

611
00:31:22,660 --> 00:31:23,530
Alright. Alright.

612
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:24,720
Leaders.

613
00:31:25,010 --> 00:31:26,080
In this case,

614
00:31:26,630 --> 00:31:28,200
I have an advice.

615
00:31:28,330 --> 00:31:29,050
Let’s

616
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:31,110
ask Mr. Shang and Mr. Yuan

617
00:31:31,140 --> 00:31:32,770
to perform for us. How about it?

618
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:36,120
Sure. Sure.

619
00:31:36,450 --> 00:31:37,960
Sure. Sure.

620
00:31:42,660 --> 00:31:44,690
It’s up to Mr. Yuan.

621
00:31:45,290 --> 00:31:46,930
Ms. Yu and I are both guests.

622
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:48,930
We shouldn’t steal the show.

623
00:31:49,970 --> 00:31:52,890
Mr. Shang. You’re too kind.

624
00:31:55,090 --> 00:31:57,530
That’s my honor.

625
00:31:58,060 --> 00:31:59,890
If so, Ms. Yu and I may perform.

626
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:10,930
Mrs. Yuan. Please.

627
00:32:17,030 --> 00:32:17,890
Don’t stand.

628
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:19,840
Sit and watch the show.

629
00:32:20,210 --> 00:32:21,170
Come. Come.

630
00:32:21,210 --> 00:32:22,000
Sit.

631
00:32:25,580 --> 00:32:26,600
Sit. Cheng.

632
00:32:31,340 --> 00:32:32,650
Sit. Sit.

633
00:32:33,970 --> 00:32:34,690
Ms. Yu.

634
00:32:35,370 --> 00:32:37,080
Jade Hairpin was performed.

635
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:38,570
Should we perform another show?

636
00:32:39,540 --> 00:32:40,450
Yes.

637
00:32:40,820 --> 00:32:42,290
We should both know it.

638
00:32:42,970 --> 00:32:44,080
We may perform...

639
00:32:45,130 --> 00:32:46,120
Perform...

640
00:32:46,940 --> 00:32:48,050
Lady Thirteen.

641
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:04,540
♫ I admire your beauty and temperament ♫

642
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:19,460
♫ Would you be my sworn sister ♫

643
00:33:24,140 --> 00:33:30,340
♫ I’m willing to be your sworn sister ♫

644
00:33:31,340 --> 00:33:36,420
♫ I’m 17 years old ♫

645
00:33:37,860 --> 00:33:49,420
♫ Zhang Jinfeng is 16 years old ♫

646
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:53,660
♫ Oh, you’re one year younger than me ♫

647
00:33:53,940 --> 00:33:55,740
♫ You’re my elder sister ♫

648
00:33:55,980 --> 00:33:57,540
♫ I’m your elder sister, of course ♫

649
00:33:58,140 --> 00:34:02,060
♫ Let’s kowtow to father and mother ♫

650
00:34:06,210 --> 00:34:08,040
Mr. Shang. Thanks for helping me.

651
00:34:08,810 --> 00:34:10,080
It's very kind of you.

652
00:34:10,370 --> 00:34:12,560
I dislike Sixi’er.

653
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:14,929
But I do want to

654
00:34:14,940 --> 00:34:17,210
invite you to perform a new opera with me.

655
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:19,730
That’s a big deal.

656
00:34:20,900 --> 00:34:22,080
I need to think about it.

657
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:24,449
You may think fast.

658
00:34:24,850 --> 00:34:26,210
If you can come,

659
00:34:26,520 --> 00:34:28,250
your salary will be the highest,

660
00:34:28,540 --> 00:34:29,840
no less than me.

661
00:34:31,530 --> 00:34:32,989
I don’t care about money.

662
00:34:33,940 --> 00:34:35,409
It’s rare for performers

663
00:34:36,659 --> 00:34:39,560
to have a good opera of our own.

664
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:42,840
Performance is one aspect,

665
00:34:43,889 --> 00:34:45,449
the script is the other.

666
00:34:47,420 --> 00:34:48,730
My new opera

667
00:34:49,330 --> 00:34:51,889
will be a classic, too.

668
00:34:54,980 --> 00:34:56,840
The Tale of Dragon you told me

669
00:34:59,090 --> 00:35:00,520
was wonderful indeed.

670
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:05,690
Alright.

671
00:35:06,850 --> 00:35:08,210
I'm grateful for your kindness.

672
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:10,280
I agree.

673
00:35:12,150 --> 00:35:13,550
You know I'm strict.

674
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,140
When you perform with me,

675
00:35:15,540 --> 00:35:16,660
I’ll nitpick.

676
00:35:17,670 --> 00:35:18,700
Just do it.

677
00:35:30,740 --> 00:35:32,350
You’re so happy.

678
00:35:32,910 --> 00:35:34,310
Yu Qing must have agreed.

679
00:35:34,520 --> 00:35:35,460
She agreed.

680
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:37,940
What’s going on

681
00:35:38,830 --> 00:35:41,110
between Yu Qing and Yuan Xiaodi?

682
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:44,420
Isn’t it normal for her to perform with master?

683
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:47,620
Why did Mrs. Yuan get mad?

684
00:35:48,190 --> 00:35:49,460
You don’t know.

685
00:35:50,180 --> 00:35:51,360
Yu Qing

686
00:35:51,770 --> 00:35:54,280
is a lady from a literary family.

687
00:35:54,570 --> 00:35:56,600
She was obsessed with Yuan Xiaodi,

688
00:35:56,790 --> 00:35:58,410
so she learnt operas .

689
00:35:58,530 --> 00:36:00,890
She even broke up with her family.

690
00:36:01,260 --> 00:36:02,320
Her skills

691
00:36:02,330 --> 00:36:04,480
were taught by Yuan Xiaodi himself.

692
00:36:04,870 --> 00:36:07,010
Then Yuan Xiaodi got married.

693
00:36:07,660 --> 00:36:09,040
She was reluctant to be his concubine.

694
00:36:09,370 --> 00:36:10,560
So, they didn't get together.

695
00:36:11,370 --> 00:36:13,040
But I don’t know

696
00:36:13,050 --> 00:36:14,080
about their situation now.

697
00:36:16,100 --> 00:36:17,840
Now you should know.

698
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:22,250
Know what?

699
00:36:22,770 --> 00:36:24,010
From the way Yuan Xiaodi

700
00:36:24,530 --> 00:36:26,120
looked at Yu Qing

701
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:28,120
when they performed,

702
00:36:30,090 --> 00:36:31,720
he loved Yu Qing.

703
00:36:33,050 --> 00:36:34,970
But Mrs. Yuan made such a scene,

704
00:36:35,130 --> 00:36:36,690
and he refused it right away.

705
00:36:37,130 --> 00:36:38,250
What does it mean?

706
00:36:38,900 --> 00:36:40,080
What?

707
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:44,450
It means they failed to be together.

708
00:36:45,240 --> 00:36:47,080
Did you see this?

709
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:49,930
Your eyes are keen indeed.

710
00:36:51,290 --> 00:36:52,800
Mr. Shang,

711
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:55,520
you must perform this opera well.

712
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:56,890
Or else,

713
00:36:57,440 --> 00:37:00,320
you’ll feel sorry for I’ve worked so hard.

714
00:37:01,500 --> 00:37:04,250
Many performers will be on the stage.

715
00:37:04,530 --> 00:37:06,040
I can’t make it alone.

716
00:37:06,530 --> 00:37:08,170
You have Yu Qing now.

717
00:37:08,900 --> 00:37:10,890
Only the two of us can’t make it.

718
00:37:10,980 --> 00:37:12,560
Among the performers in Shuiyun Theater,

719
00:37:13,900 --> 00:37:15,130
Liuyue left,

720
00:37:15,170 --> 00:37:16,730
and no one performs the role of young ladies well.

721
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:19,010
Shang. Cheng.

722
00:37:19,330 --> 00:37:20,600
You want performer who plays young ladies?

723
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:22,320
I know someone.

724
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:25,490
I knew this talented child not long ago.

725
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:28,600
Are you serious?

726
00:37:28,750 --> 00:37:31,010
Although Mr. Fan’s capability is limited,

727
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:33,450
he’s good at appreciating operas.

728
00:37:33,460 --> 00:37:34,320
Of course.

729
00:37:34,500 --> 00:37:36,490
I’m good at appreciating operas.

730
00:37:36,500 --> 00:37:37,450
There’s no doubt.

731
00:37:38,090 --> 00:37:40,250
Xirui. Did you notice

732
00:37:40,530 --> 00:37:42,010
the boy brought by Sixi’er

733
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:43,280
in blue rope?

734
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:45,280
I ever listened to his voice.

735
00:37:45,570 --> 00:37:47,690
His voice is good, also good-looking.

736
00:37:48,950 --> 00:37:50,360
If he is good,

737
00:37:50,570 --> 00:37:52,010
he should have debuted.

738
00:37:52,260 --> 00:37:55,080
Cheng. Sixi’er doesn’t like him.

739
00:37:55,090 --> 00:37:56,490
He beats or scolds him every day.

740
00:37:56,900 --> 00:37:58,360
How come he debuts easily?

741
00:37:59,090 --> 00:38:01,690
If it’s Sixi’er, it’s not surprising.

742
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:03,120
He gets old,

743
00:38:03,380 --> 00:38:04,730
and is jealous

744
00:38:04,970 --> 00:38:07,580
of good-looking young apprentices.

745
00:38:13,980 --> 00:38:16,870
Will you be like this when you get old?

746
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:18,080
I won’t be old.

747
00:38:18,500 --> 00:38:19,790
When I’m in my forties,

748
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:21,210
I’ll hang myself.

749
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:23,080
Both you and I can be relieved.

750
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:32,650
Where does he perform? Let’s go to watch.

751
00:38:32,830 --> 00:38:34,040
Sixi’er doesn’t allow him to perform.

752
00:38:34,210 --> 00:38:35,210
We can’t see him.

753
00:38:36,500 --> 00:38:38,120
Let’s go to Yunxi Theater to see him.

754
00:38:46,530 --> 00:38:47,600
Here we are.

755
00:38:48,460 --> 00:38:49,490
His master Sixi’er

756
00:38:49,500 --> 00:38:50,360
is fierce and mean.

757
00:38:50,370 --> 00:38:51,450
I dare not offend him.

758
00:38:52,370 --> 00:38:54,080
You... You may go inside.

759
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:56,360
I don't know Zhouzi.

760
00:38:56,370 --> 00:38:57,360
It doesn’t matter.

761
00:38:57,510 --> 00:38:59,890
He is working in the yard.

762
00:39:00,810 --> 00:39:01,410
Could you

763
00:39:02,050 --> 00:39:03,760
keep watch at the door for us?

764
00:39:03,770 --> 00:39:05,930
OK. I’ll keep watch here for you.

765
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:07,170
Thank you.

766
00:39:21,370 --> 00:39:22,280
Listen, Cheng.

767
00:39:29,770 --> 00:39:44,360
♫ So I just pick up reed catkins at the wilderness ♫

768
00:39:44,370 --> 00:39:45,720
What a pity.

769
00:39:51,180 --> 00:39:52,100
Mr. Shang.

770
00:39:55,700 --> 00:39:56,760
Mr. Shang.

771
00:39:57,860 --> 00:39:59,040
Are you Zhouzi?

772
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:05,170
Someone advised me to listen to your opera.

773
00:40:09,350 --> 00:40:10,600
What happened to your face?

774
00:40:10,850 --> 00:40:11,520
Nothing.

775
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:14,060
I fell down.

776
00:40:14,390 --> 00:40:16,280
You got fingerprints by falling?

777
00:40:17,370 --> 00:40:19,250
That's too much.

778
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:22,890
He’s beaten too hard.

779
00:40:24,170 --> 00:40:26,830
Mr. Shang. You said it’s a pity.

780
00:40:27,050 --> 00:40:29,680
Do you mean I didn't sing well?

781
00:40:31,290 --> 00:40:32,560
Not like that.

782
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:35,560
Your timbre is like Sixi’er’s a lot,

783
00:40:35,900 --> 00:40:37,120
but he didn’t teach you well.

784
00:40:38,060 --> 00:40:39,360
Listen to my voice.

785
00:40:41,530 --> 00:40:55,450
♫ I can’t put up with the torture from stepmother ♫

786
00:40:55,700 --> 00:41:11,320
♫ So I just pick up reed catkins at the wilderness ♫

787
00:41:11,930 --> 00:41:13,620
Mr. Shang. How come you're singing?

788
00:41:13,650 --> 00:41:15,250
Sixi’er may hear you.

789
00:41:15,270 --> 00:41:17,080
It’s fine. I won’t make trouble. I’m leaving.

790
00:41:17,160 --> 00:41:18,210
Cheng. Let's go.

791
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:21,350
Mr. Shang.

792
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:22,930
-I beg you.
-Rise.

793
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:24,410
Please help me. Please save me.

794
00:41:24,420 --> 00:41:25,080
Get up.

795
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:28,380
Mr. Shang. Please buy me out.

796
00:41:28,530 --> 00:41:29,650
I can earn money for you.

797
00:41:31,060 --> 00:41:32,970
Mr. Shang. Only if I follow you,

798
00:41:33,370 --> 00:41:34,600
can I perform.

799
00:41:35,310 --> 00:41:37,010
Follow me and perform?

800
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:39,010
You’ll never perform.

801
00:41:39,700 --> 00:41:41,730
You have no backbone.

802
00:41:41,930 --> 00:41:43,970
How can you be a star on stage?

803
00:41:44,980 --> 00:41:45,890
Get up.

804
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:50,210
If you want,

805
00:41:50,950 --> 00:41:53,010
sneak out and come to me in the future.

806
00:41:53,460 --> 00:41:54,450
I’ll teach you.

807
00:41:56,890 --> 00:41:57,260
Mr. Shang.

808
00:41:57,270 --> 00:41:58,080
Get up.

809
00:41:58,090 --> 00:41:59,580
Why do you kneel again?

810
00:41:59,600 --> 00:42:01,170
Mr. Shang. Leave now.

811
00:42:01,180 --> 00:42:02,690
If Sixi’er sees this,

812
00:42:02,700 --> 00:42:03,800
he’ll have a row with you

813
00:42:03,810 --> 00:42:04,810
-Rest assured.
-and make a scene.

814
00:42:05,530 --> 00:42:06,730
I’ll take care of it.

815
00:42:07,330 --> 00:42:09,360
He’s talented. I’m reluctant

816
00:42:09,810 --> 00:42:10,840
to see him suffer in Yunxi Theater.

817
00:42:11,590 --> 00:42:12,320
Go.

818
00:42:12,810 --> 00:42:13,760
Fine. Hurry.

819
00:42:13,770 --> 00:42:15,360
Go to wash clothes now.
